Edge AI Prototype – Recyclable Item Classifier
Goal
Train a lightweight CNN to classify recyclable items (e.g., plastic, metal, paper, glass), convert to TensorFlow Lite, and evaluate.

Tools Used
Python, TensorFlow/Keras
TensorFlow Lite Converter
Google Colab (simulation environment)
Dataset: TrashNet (public dataset of ~2,500 labeled waste images)
Code Implementation (Colab-Compatible)
python
