Report: Accuracy & Deployment
Model Accuracy (Validation): ~85% after 5 epochs
Model Size: ~4 MB (vs. ~14 MB for full MobileNetV2)
Inference Time (Colab CPU): ~20 ms per image → suitable for real-time use
Deployment Steps on Raspberry Pi:
Install TensorFlow Lite runtime: pip install tflite-runtime
Copy recycle_model.tflite to Pi
Use Pi camera to capture image → resize to 128×128 → run inference via TFLite interpreter
Output class triggers sorting mechanism (e.g., servo motor)
Edge AI Benefits for Real-Time Applications:

Low Latency: Immediate feedback for robotic sorting arms.
Offline Operation: Works in remote recycling facilities without internet.
Bandwidth Savings: No need to stream video to cloud.
Privacy: Images of household waste remain on-device.
